data.title: All of The Games on Netflix Right Now - Netflix Tudum
data.meta_description: From Hades, to Grand Theft Auto III - The Definitive Editions, there are more than 90 mobile games available for Netflix members to play at no additional cost.
data.text:
‎

By Tudum Staff

Aug. 27, 2024

Netflix members have access to more than 80 exclusive mobile games with no ads, no extra fees, and no in-app purchases. The games are free and easily downloaded from your favorite app store to your Android phones and tablets as well as iPhone, iPad, and iPod touch.

So, clear your schedule and check out the full list of available games below:

Featured

Netflix Stories: Emily in Paris

"Emily in Paris" — Say “oui” to possibility. Follow your heart and live out your own story set in the City of Love in this interactive story based on the hit series.

Table Top

About

First time downloading a game? No worries. We’ve got all the information you’ll need to get started playing.

Here’s the important stuff: Netflix games can be downloaded and played on mobile devices, including Android phones and tablets and iPhone, iPad, and iPod touch. Games are accessed through your Netflix account and profile.

IMPORTANT NOTE:

Netflix games aren’t available for Kids profiles.

Don’t worry about losing your leveled-up characters. Progress made in Netflix Games is saved to the profile associated with your gameplay, and is retained either through cloud saves or locally on your device.

ANOTHER IMPORTANT NOTE:

Progress or saved data from games previously released can’t be transferred to the Netflix version of a game.

Want to know the kind of game you’re playing and whether it might be appropriate? Netflix games have a maturity rating, so you can make informed gameplay choices for you and your family.

As with downloaded TV shows and movies, games can be played on multiple devices on the same account. If you hit your device limit, we’ll let you know. To free up a slot, sign out of devices not in use.

Device Requirements

You’ll need a compatible device that is one of the following:

Android phone or tablet running Android 8.0 or later

iPhone, iPad, or iPod touch running iOS/iPadOS 15 or later

An active Netflix subscription

An internet connection to download and install the game

Enough storage space on your device

A childlike wonder of games and good times (not actually necessary).

ONE LAST IMPORTANT NOTE:

Some Netflix Games might have additional requirements that aren’t outlined above. If there are, we’ll let you know in the game’s app page.
